data.description: Welcome to this charming four-bedroom home in McMinnville. The primary bedroom features a full bath and walk-in closet. No need to worry about parking or storage the full-sized two-car garage has you covered. And the expansive backyard is a blank slate with endless possibilities for outdoor activities and relaxation. Located near Tice Park, you'll have easy access to outdoor recreation and leisure. This home offers not just comfort, but also convenience and a great lifestyle. Don't miss out!
